-22T17:30:42.000Z","msg":"國師篇文<br />\n基本係預言左之後6年發生既狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且指出問題根源同埋警隊必然遇上既困境<br />\n7犯若早d睇左國師呢篇文<br />\n可能就唔會on99落得如此下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360e62f5a5e7081b36f93df20b597b24ca23feeb","tid":130904,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea53ffeeed81307469422cc5ff12032be0879303","tid":130904,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47fdc92cea42188f3abecee4e76b584c2e27b622","tid":130904,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"國師又中！國師再中！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實國師一早預到今時今日個政治局勢有本土堀起之勢。"},{"pid":"cac06fba425eeb9d5585540d544f12956ffca664","tid":130904,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦，我可以好撚肯定就算用返港英手法對付返近年既大型示威，都一定會話警察黑警。<br />\n<br />\n教育比以前普及左，多左人識點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29c4c919be6bb56e89f1c722280c4e4bb86df9f","tid":130904,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"黑警以前就冇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年強姦，以前貪污，賤種華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f25a539502e771b66f97b3b6e9658c9d65665c4","tid":130904,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:09:34.000Z","msg":"國師頭一句咪答左你囉<br />\n咪就係政府以不義之名，唆使警察陷害忠良<br />\n如果跟法<br />\n香港警察係有責任協助大型示威<br />\n唔係開催淚彈啡 9市民<br />\n你開催淚彈一刻已經唔係警察喇<br />\n禍根早就種下<br />\n之後做乜撚野都會有認受性"},{"pid":"aa6f4fd80670b8d4323427b7aa8a01572606d186","tid":130904,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0